commit.message:
pa.h (ASM_OUTPUT_FUNCTION_PREFIX): Don't surround section names with '$'.

        * pa.h (ASM_OUTPUT_FUNCTION_PREFIX): Don't surround section names
        with '$'.  That confuses collect2.
        (ASM_OUTPUT_SECTION_NAME): Likewise.

From-SVN: r10794
